{
  "name": "ColorScaleCriterion",
  "summary": "<p>每个 <strong>ColorScaleCriterion</strong> 都是 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/ColorScaleCriteria/ColorScaleCriteria .htm#ColorScaleCriteria.ColorScaleCriteria\">ColorScaleCriteria</a></strong> 集合的一部分。使用 <strong>ColorScaleCriteria</strong>(<em>index</em>) 可以返回单独的条件。</p>\n<p>您可以设置色阶的每个阈值的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/ColorScaleCriterion/ColorScaleCriterion .htm#ColorScaleCriterion.Type\">Type</a></strong>、<strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/ColorScaleCriterion/ColorScaleCriterion .htm#ColorScaleCriterion.Value\">Value</a></strong> 和 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/ColorScaleCriterion/ColorScaleCriterion .htm#ColorScaleCriterion.FormatColor\">FormatColor</a></strong>。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例创建了一个数字范围，然后将双色色阶条件格式规则应用于该范围。然后通过在ColorScaleCriteria集合中编制索引来设置单独的条件，从而指定最小阈值的颜色为红色，最大阈值的颜色为蓝色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// Fill cells with sample data from 1 to 10</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C2&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1:C2&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AutoFill</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1:C10&quot;</span>))\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1:C10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Select</span>()\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// Create a two-color ColorScale object for the created sample data range</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorScale = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddColorScale</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// Set the minimum threshold to red and maximum threshold to blue</span>\n    colorScale.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorScaleCriteria</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatColor</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>)\n    colorScale.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorScaleCriteria</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatColor</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断如果第一张工作表上单元格区域 A1:A10 的第一个色阶条件格式的第一个阈值条件的类型为xlConditionValueNumber，则设置该阈值条件的值和填充颜色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorScale = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> criterion = colorScale.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorScaleCriteria</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (criterion.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span> == xlConditionValueNumber) {\n        criterion.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>\n        criterion.<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatColor</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorIndex</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">8</span>\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>代表颜色格式条件格式的最小、中点或最大阈值的条件。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "FormatColor",
      "summary": "<p>通过使用 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/FormatColor/FormatColor .htm#FormatColor.Color\">Color</a></strong> 属性，您可以将最小、中点或最大阈值的颜色设置为任何自定义的颜色；或者使用 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/FormatColor/FormatColor .htm#FormatColor.ThemeColor\">ThemeColor</a></strong> 属性。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/FormatColor/FormatColor .htm#FormatColor.FormatColor\">FormatColor</a></strong> 对象，该对象指定分配给色阶条件格式的阈值的颜色。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置活动工作表上单元格区域 A1:A10 的第二个色阶条件格式的阈值条件的颜色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorScale = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    colorScale.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorScaleCriteria</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatColor</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Color</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>)\n    colorScale.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorScaleCriteria</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatColor</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorIndex</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">7</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断如果活动工作表上单元格区域 A1:A10 的第一个色阶条件格式的第二个阈值条件的类型为xlConditionValueHighestValue，则设置该阈值条件的主题颜色和亮度。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorScale = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> criterion = colorScale.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorScaleCriteria</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (criterion.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span> == xlConditionValueHighestValue) {\n        criterion.<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatColor</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ThemeColor</span> = xlThemeColorAccent6\n        criterion.<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatColor</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TintAndShade</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0.5</span>\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "FormatColor",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Index",
      "summary": "<p>对于双色色阶条件格式规则，此属性将为最小阈值返回值“1”，为最大阈值返回值“2”。在使用三色色阶规则时，最小、中点和最大阈值的值将分别为“1”、“2”和“3”。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong>Long</strong> 值，该值表示条件代表的阈值。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表上单元格区域 A1:A10 的第一个色阶条件格式的第一个阈值条件的索引。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorScale = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> criterion = colorScale.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorScaleCriteria</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(criterion.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Index</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将第一张工作表上单元格区域 A1:A10 的第二个色阶条件格式的所有阈值条件的索引赋值到活动工作表的单元格中。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorScale = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; i &lt;= colorScale.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorScaleCriteria</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>; i++) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Cells</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i, <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = colorScale.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorScaleCriteria</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Index</span>\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Type",
      "summary": "<p>数据条或色阶的阈值类型可以是数字、百分比、公式或百分点值。如果将类型设置为百分点值，将使用 ET 中的 Percentile 函数确定阈值。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回 <strong><a href=\"topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/枚举/XlConditionValueTypes 枚举.html\">XlConditionValueTypes</a></strong> 枚举的常量之一，该常量指定如何确定数据栏或色标条件格式的阈值。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第一张工作表上单元格区域 A1:A5 的第一个色阶条件格式的第二个阈值条件的类型是否为xlConditionValuePercentile。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorScale = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A5&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> criterion = colorScale.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorScaleCriteria</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(criterion.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span> == xlConditionValuePercentile)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断如果活动工作表上单元格区域 A1:A10 的第二个色阶条件格式的阈值条件的类型为xlConditionValueNumber，则通知用户。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorScale = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; i &lt;= colorScale.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorScaleCriteria</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>; i++) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> criterion = colorScale.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorScaleCriteria</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i)\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (criterion.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span> == xlConditionValueNumber) {\n            <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">`第 <span class=\"hljs-subst\">${i}</span> 个阈值条件的类型为 xlConditionValueNumber。`</span>)\n        }\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "XlConditionValueTypes",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Value",
      "summary": "<p>仅当条件格式的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/ColorScaleCriterion/ColorScaleCriterion .htm#ColorScaleCriterion.Type\">ColorScaleCriterion.Type</a></strong> 属性设置为常量 <strong>xlConditionValueNumber</strong>、<strong>xlConditionValuePercent</strong>、<strong>xlConditionValuePercentile</strong> 或 <strong>xlConditionValueFormula</strong> 时，才能设置该值。</p>\n<p>如果阈值类型为公式，则可以将公式设置为 <strong>String</strong> 类型。而公式必须返回单个数字。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置色阶条件格式的最小、中点或最大阈值。可读/写 <strong>Variant</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表上单元格区域 A1:A10 的第一个色阶条件格式的第一个阈值条件的值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorScale = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A10&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> criterion = colorScale.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorScaleCriteria</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(criterion.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断如果第一张工作表上单元格区域 A1:A5 的第一个色阶条件格式的第三个阈值条件的类型为xlConditionValueNumber，则将该阈值条件的值设置为5。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> colorScale = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:A5&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FormatConditions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> criterion = colorScale.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorScaleCriteria</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (criterion.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span> == xlConditionValueNumber) {\n        criterion.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">5</span>\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "any",
      "readonly": false
    }
  ],
  "functions": []
}